CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 14, 1961, pg. 17, reads: "The Mt. Horum Singers - Mt. Rose Baptist Church, 1901 Wylie Ave., will be the site of the fifth anniversary of the Mt. Horum Singers on Oct. 15, at 3:30 P.M. All local groups are invited to attend. The Laura White Prayer Band will lead the devotions. The Rev. J. H. Hunter is host pastor."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of The Mt. Horum Singers with five women, and two men, including one with "S" monogram on collar, gathered around piano
